01:54:51,176 --> 01:54:53,304
你先聽我說
I need you to listen to me.

1291
01:54:54,388 --> 01:54:55,639
我是你爸爸
As your father,

1292
01:54:55,723 --> 01:54:57,349
我求你了
I'm begging you.

1293
01:55:03,272 --> 01:55:05,107
要是我爸爸就一定懂我
If you'd been a real dad,

1294
01:55:05,190 --> 01:55:07,818
懂得聖盃在哪
you'd know me well enough to imagine where the Cup is,

1295
01:55:07,902 --> 01:55:10,529
知道我心底想的地方
where my deepest thoughts are taking it.

1296
01:55:11,822 --> 01:55:14,617
你一點都不懂我
You don't know the first thing about me.

1297
01:55:15,534 --> 01:55:17,328
你不是我爸…
You're not my dad...

1298
01:55:18,704 --> 01:55:20,539
永遠不是
And you never will be.

1299
01:55:20,623 --> 01:55:22,875
我保證你不會再見到我
I promise, you'll never have to see me again.

1300
01:55:29,423 --> 01:55:30,633
克拉蕾，謝謝
Thank you, Clary.

1301
01:55:35,262 --> 01:55:38,307
沒有聖盃，我們會輸的
Without this Cup, we are lost.

1302
01:55:39,266 --> 01:55:40,517
不是「我們」
Not "we."

1303
01:55:42,811 --> 01:55:43,854
是你
You.

1304
01:56:08,796 --> 01:56:09,964
克拉蕾！
Clary!

1305
01:56:13,050 --> 01:56:15,177
- 不！抓住我！  - 決不！
- No! Don't let go! - Never!

1306
01:56:18,305 --> 01:56:19,390
這兒！
Here!

1307
01:57:18,323 --> 01:57:19,783
你還好嗎？
Are you okay?

1308
01:57:20,617 --> 01:57:22,119
我不知道
I don't know.

1309
01:58:01,784 --> 01:58:04,411
我知道你之前為什麼那樣做了
I understand why you did what you did.

1310
01:58:06,663 --> 01:58:08,332
我原諒你
And I forgive you.

1311
01:58:09,708 --> 01:58:11,668
我要你知道
I want you to know,

1312
01:58:13,754 --> 01:58:15,881
我會為你保密
your secret's safe with me.

1313
01:59:09,643 --> 01:59:12,187
她怎麼樣了？
So, how's she doing?

1314
01:59:12,896 --> 01:59:14,064
情況穩定了
Stable.

1315
01:59:14,731 --> 01:59:16,775
醫生不知道她喝過什麼
The doctors don't know what she took,

1316
01:59:16,859 --> 01:59:19,069
只能等
so we just have to wait.

1317
01:59:22,739 --> 01:59:24,491
對不起
I'm sorry.

1318
01:59:24,575 --> 01:59:26,535
我覺得我只是一個老古董
I guess I'm an old romantic.

1319
01:59:26,618 --> 01:59:28,829
我總希望當我向某人說
I always hoped that when I finally said

1320
01:59:28,912 --> 01:59:32,082
「我愛你」時，她會說同樣的話
"I love you" to someone, she'd say the same thing back.

1321
01:59:32,541 --> 01:59:34,334
那個人會的
And that someone will.

1322
01:59:34,418 --> 01:59:35,752
但願吧
Yeah, I know.

1323
01:59:44,928 --> 01:59:46,597
你很累了
Hey, you're tired.

1324
01:59:46,680 --> 01:59:49,099
去休息吧，我們會照看好她
Go sleep, we'll take care of her.

1325
01:59:50,267 --> 01:59:51,768
好，抱一個
Yeah, come on.

1326
02:00:43,237 --> 02:00:45,280
我喜歡你收拾這
I like what you've done with the place.

1327
02:00:45,364 --> 02:00:47,824
我只是耍了些把戲
I've got a few tricks up my sleeve.

1328
02:00:49,618 --> 02:00:51,787
克拉蕾，我們真怕你不會回來了
Clary, we're afraid you're not coming back.

1329
02:00:53,330 --> 02:00:54,915
只是現在跟你作伴真的很難
It's just really hard to be around you right now.

1330
02:00:54,998 --> 02:00:57,000
對我來說也一樣
It's hard for me as well.

1331
02:00:58,335 --> 02:01:00,671
但是這不僅僅是我們
But this is about more than us.

1332
02:01:01,964 --> 02:01:04,883
你有不可思議的天賦，我們需要你
You have an incredible gift, and we need you.

1333
02:01:07,970 --> 02:01:09,346
我需要你
I need you.

1334
02:01:10,514 --> 02:01:12,182
我不知道
I just don't know.

1335
02:01:12,849 --> 02:01:15,018
還記得我說過從沒見過天使？
Remember when I said I'd never seen an angel?

1336
02:01:19,231 --> 02:01:20,691
我撒謊了
Well, I lied.

1337
02:01:30,242 --> 02:01:32,244
你是我見過最勇敢的凡人
You're still the bravest mundane I've ever met.

1338
02:01:36,707 --> 02:01:38,375
我可不是凡人
I'm not a mundane.

1339
02:01:41,003 --> 02:01:42,170
等等，傑斯！
Wait, Jace!

1340
02:01:46,508 --> 02:01:47,759
慢慢來啊
You took your time.

1341
02:01:54,725 --> 02:01:56,643
你說過你需要我
You said you needed me.

1342
02:02:01,606 --> 02:02:03,066
你該好好保存它
You should keep that safe.

1343
02:02:03,150 --> 02:02:04,276
我會的
Yeah.

1344
02:02:05,902 --> 02:02:07,612
我可以抱著你嗎…
Is it okay if I...

1345
02:02:08,572 --> 02:02:09,990
我能…
Do I...

1346
02:02:10,073 --> 02:02:12,242
- 這樣可以嗎…  - 沒關係
- Is it okay if I... - Yeah.

1347
02:02:15,495 --> 02:02:17,748
聽著，克拉蕾，我不相信它
Look, Clary, I don't believe it.

1348
02:02:17,831 --> 02:02:19,541
這似乎不是真的，不在我的心
It doesn't feel like the truth, not in my heart.

1349
02:02:21,168 --> 02:02:24,254
我只是不懂如何去面對這個世界
I just don't know how to look at the world anymore.

1350
02:02:24,338 --> 02:02:27,132
我看不到街道，紅綠燈和車
I don't see streets and traffic lights and cars.

1351
02:02:27,215 --> 02:02:29,176
眼前只是邪靈和天使
I see demons and angels.

1352
02:02:30,135 --> 02:02:31,136
一切都變了
Everything's different.

1353
02:02:31,219 --> 02:02:33,013
世界還是一樣的
The world's the same.

1354
02:02:33,930 --> 02:02:36,224
你才是變了的那個
You're the one who's different.

1355
02:02:42,439 --> 02:02:44,066
你還記得霍奇說的嗎？
Don't you remember what Hodge said?

1356
02:02:44,149 --> 02:02:45,359
什麼？
What?

1357
02:02:45,442 --> 02:02:47,110
所以故事都是真的
All the stories are true.

1358
02:03:00,587 --> 02:03:03,158
感謝觀影
